{"id":43,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":43,"title":"D&C 39","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 39"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet to James Covel, at Fayette, New York, January 5, 1831. James Covel, who had been a Methodist minister for about forty years, covenanted with the Lord that he would obey any command that the Lord would give to him through Joseph the Prophet."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.1-4"},"1–4"],", The Saints have power to become the sons of God;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.5-6"},"5–6"],", To receive the gospel is to receive Christ;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.7-14"},"7–14"],", James Covel is commanded to be baptized and labor in the Lord’s vineyard;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.15-21"},"15–21"],", The Lord’s servants are to preach the gospel before the Second Coming;",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.22-24"},"22–24"],", Those who receive the gospel will be gathered in time and in eternity."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.1","order":"06.05.039.4581"},["b","1"],"Hearken and listen to the voice of him who is from all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"eternity"],"to all eternity, the Great",["span.smallCaps",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"I Am"]],", even Jesus Christ—"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.2","order":"06.05.039.4582"},["b","2"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"light"],"and the life of the world; a light which shineth in darkness and the darkness comprehendeth it not;"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.3","order":"06.05.039.4583"},["b","3"],"The same which came in the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"meridian of time"],"unto mine own, and mine own",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"received me not"],";"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.4","order":"06.05.039.4584"},["b","4"],"But to as many as received me, gave I power to become my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"sons"],"; and even so will I give unto as many as will receive me, power to become my sons."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.5","order":"06.05.039.4585"},["b","5"],"And verily, verily, I say unto you, he that receiveth my gospel",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"receiveth"],"me; and he that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"receiveth"],"not my gospel receiveth not me."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.6","order":"06.05.039.4586"},["b","6"],"And this is my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"gospel"],"—repentance and baptism by water, and then cometh the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"baptism of fire"],"and the Holy Ghost, even the Comforter, which showeth all things, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"teacheth"],"the peaceable things of the kingdom."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.7","order":"06.05.039.4587"},["b","7"],"And now, behold, I say unto you, my servant",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"James"],", I have looked upon thy works and I",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"know"],"thee."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.8","order":"06.05.039.4588"},["b","8"],"And verily I say unto thee, thine heart is now right before me at this time; and, behold, I have bestowed great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"blessings"],"upon thy head;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.9","order":"06.05.039.4589"},["b","9"],"Nevertheless, thou hast seen great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"sorrow"],", for thou hast",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"rejected"],"me many times because of pride and the cares of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"world"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.10","order":"06.05.039.4590"},["b","10"],"But, behold, the days of thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"deliverance"],"are come, if thou wilt",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"hearken"],"to my voice, which saith unto thee: Arise and be baptized, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"wash"],"away your sins, calling on my name, and you shall receive my Spirit, and a blessing so great as you never have known."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.11","order":"06.05.039.4591"},["b","11"],"And if thou do this, I have prepared thee for a greater work. Thou shalt preach the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"fulness"],"of my gospel, which I have sent forth in these last days, the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"covenant"],"which I have sent forth to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_11c"},"recover"],"my people, which are of the house of Israel."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.12","order":"06.05.039.4592"},["b","12"],"And it shall come to pass that power shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"rest"],"upon thee; thou shalt have great faith, and I will be with thee and go before thy face."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.13","order":"06.05.039.4593"},["b","13"],"Thou art called to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"labor"],"in my vineyard, and to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"build"],"up my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"church"],", and to bring forth",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"Zion"],", that it may rejoice upon the hills and",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_13e"},"flourish"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.14","order":"06.05.039.4594"},["b","14"],"Behold, verily, verily, I say unto thee, thou art not called to go into the eastern countries, but thou art called to go to the Ohio."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.15","order":"06.05.039.4595"},["b","15"],"And inasmuch as my people shall assemble themselves at the Ohio, I have kept in store a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"blessing"],"such as is not known among the children of men, and it shall be poured forth upon their heads. And from thence men shall go forth into",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"all"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"nations"],"."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.16","order":"06.05.039.4596"},["b","16"],"Behold, verily, verily, I say unto you, that the people in Ohio call upon me in much faith, thinking I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"stay"],"my hand in judgment upon the nations, but I cannot",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"deny"],"my word."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.17","order":"06.05.039.4597"},["b","17"],"Wherefore lay to with your might and call faithful laborers into my vineyard, that it may be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"pruned"],"for the last time."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.18","order":"06.05.039.4598"},["b","18"],"And inasmuch as they do repent and receive the fulness of my gospel, and become sanctified, I will stay mine hand in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"judgment"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.19","order":"06.05.039.4599"},["b","19"],"Wherefore, go forth, crying with a loud voice, saying: The kingdom of heaven is at",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"hand"],"; crying: Hosanna! blessed be the name of the Most High God."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.20","order":"06.05.039.4600"},["b","20"],"Go forth",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"baptizing"],"with water, preparing the way before my face for the time of my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"coming"],";"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.21","order":"06.05.039.4601"},["b","21"],"For the time is at hand; the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"day"],"or the hour no man",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"knoweth"],"; but it surely shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_21c"},"come"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.22","order":"06.05.039.4602"},["b","22"],"And he that receiveth these things receiveth me; and they shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"gathered"],"unto me in time and in eternity."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.23","order":"06.05.039.4603"},["b","23"],"And again, it shall come to pass that on as many as ye shall baptize with water, ye shall lay your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"hands"],", and they shall receive the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"gift"],"of the Holy Ghost, and shall be",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"looking"],"forth for the signs of my",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_23d"},"coming"],", and shall know me."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.24","order":"06.05.039.4604"},["b","24"],"Behold, I come quickly. Even so. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.1a","order":"06.05.039.4605"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/13.8"},"Heb. 13:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.12"},"D&C 20:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/35.1"},"35:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.1.1-4"},"38:1 (1–4)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.4"},"76:4"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/eternity"},"TG Eternity"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.1b","order":"06.05.039.4607"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/3.14"},"Ex. 3:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/44.6"},"Isa. 44:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/1.8"},"Rev. 1:8"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-jehovah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Jehovah"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.2a","order":"06.05.039.4609"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-light-of-the-world"},"TG Jesus Christ, Light of the World"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.3a","order":"06.05.039.4611"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.26"},"D&C 20:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/5.57"},"Moses 5:57"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/6.57.57,62"},"6:57 (57, 62)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.46"},"7:46"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.3b","order":"06.05.039.4613"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-rejection-of"},"TG Prophets, Rejection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.4a","order":"06.05.039.4615"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/1.12"},"John 1:12"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sons-and-daughters-of-god"},"TG Sons and Daughters of God"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.5a","order":"06.05.039.4617"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.20"},"John 13:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.5b","order":"06.05.039.4619"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/teachable"},"TG Teachable"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.6a","order":"06.05.039.4621"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism"},"TG Baptism"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/gospel"},"Gospel"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.6b","order":"06.05.039.4623"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-baptism-of"},"TG Holy Ghost, Baptism of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-comforter"},"Holy Ghost, Comforter"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holy-ghost-mission-of"},"Holy Ghost, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.6c","order":"06.05.039.4625"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/36.2"},"D&C 36:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.61"},"42:61"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.7a","order":"06.05.039.4627"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/40.1"},"D&C 40:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.7b","order":"06.05.039.4629"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/18.19"},"Gen. 18:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.8a","order":"06.05.039.4631"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/10.6"},"Prov. 10:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.9a","order":"06.05.039.4633"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/7.29"},"Mosiah 7:29"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.9b","order":"06.05.039.4635"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/12.48"},"John 12:48"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/10.6"},"Alma 10:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.9c","order":"06.05.039.4637"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/13.22"},"Matt. 13:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/7.5"},"Hel. 7:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.10a","order":"06.05.039.4639"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.10b","order":"06.05.039.4641"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/40.3.1-3"},"D&C 40:3 (1–3)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.10c","order":"06.05.039.4643"},["b","10c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/baptism-essential"},"TG Baptism, Essential"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/purity"},"Purity"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.11a","order":"06.05.039.4645"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/15.29"},"Rom. 15:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.4"},"D&C 18:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.11b","order":"06.05.039.4647"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.22"},"D&C 1:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"11c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.11c","order":"06.05.039.4649"},["b","11c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-restoration-of"},"TG Israel, Restoration of"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.12a","order":"06.05.039.4651"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/12.9"},"2 Cor. 12:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deliver"},"TG Deliver"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/guidance-divine"},"Guidance, Divine"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.13a","order":"06.05.039.4653"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/20.8.1-16"},"Matt. 20:8 (1–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.13b","order":"06.05.039.4655"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/30.6"},"D&C 30:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.8"},"42:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"13c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.13c","order":"06.05.039.4657"},["b","13c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-head-of-the-church"},"TG Jesus Christ, Head of the Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"13d","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/39.13d","order":"06.05.039.4659"},["b","13d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/52.8"},"Isa. 52:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"13e","uri":"/scri